{"tid":501170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"來港8年仍未適應　新移民婦墜樓亡","createTime":"2017-12-16T14:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T16:49:45.000Z","uid":5195,"like":374,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"30c19f1ee60e56d1db588463f3562b904213c46f","tid":501170,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:28:00.000Z","msg":"沙田廣林苑發生墮樓案，下午1時許，姓羅(35歲)女子危坐馥林閣19樓走廊欄杆，附近居民見狀報警。當消防及警員到場時，發現女子已墮樓，昏迷倒臥大廈對開，經救護員檢查後證實她已死亡，警方在場發現遺書，正調查事件原因，死者丈夫和其8歲女兒，事後到場認屍。<br />\n<br />\n死者一名男友人聞訊趕抵現場，指死者丈夫從事運輸業，兩人育有一女。死者雖然來港已8年，並剛取得香港永久性居民身份證，但一直未能適應香港生活，估計因而輕生。"},{"pid":"d81b94c9877a8b546d0294f3ad2d0097f4bca58d","tid":501170,"uid":53524,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:31:37.000Z","msg":"似係太興奮"},{"pid":"6d95fd1f6c3af19c6ff7dc8cd8c0456c08e4165c","tid":501170,"uid":56240,"like":75,"dislike":4,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:35:38.000Z","msg":"好!死得一件得一件<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但日日黎幾百件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4623c1782ac848a53f1b25d749cbffcac1a0769","tid":501170,"uid":78429,"like":336,"dislike":6,"score":330,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:38:18.000Z","msg":"識跳樓代表已經適應咗"},{"pid":"b129a398b887301fcfcfa8b57e54734bd40eaa68","tid":501170,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識跳樓代表已經適應咗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92656a2410e46913b6a10e7bb186b9b096fd6e5e","tid":501170,"uid":90601,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T14:41:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>識跳樓代表已經適應咗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又好似有啲道理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n祖国那么先進 為何要來香港？"},{"pid":"5c150eec37a04aa27bc4facfc